# Odoo.sh Staging Environment

**Effective: 2026-03-31**

## Staging Instance

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **URL** | `https://cryptoxdog-ib-odoo-19-staging-30217068.dev.odoo.com` |
| **Build ID** | `30217068` |
